read document properties

Source: R/read_docx.R
doc_properties.Rd

read Word or PowerPoint document properties and get results in a data.frame.

doc_properties(x)

Arguments

x

an rdocx or rpptx object

See also

Other functions for Word document informations: docx_bookmarks(), docx_dim(), length.rdocx(), set_doc_properties(), styles_info()

Examples

x <- read_docx()
doc_properties(x)

#>               tag                value
#> 1           title                     
#> 2         subject                     
#> 3         creator                     
#> 4        keywords                     
#> 5     description                     
#> 6  lastModifiedBy          David Gohel
#> 7        revision                    9
#> 8         created 2017-02-28T11:18:00Z
#> 9        modified 2020-05-13T09:11:00Z
#> 10       category
